- Jordy N. texted
for everybody,

24:16.256 --> 24:18.324
"Why did most of the crew
continue to defend

24:18.358 --> 24:21.061
"Mathew over Lexi,
especially considering

24:21.061 --> 24:23.697
"he said some pretty terrible
things as well?"

