Anyone want to take this?

24:25.665 --> 24:27.500
- So I feel like
we were pretty stern

24:27.534 --> 24:30.236
with both of them about
how-how the situation was,

24:30.270 --> 24:33.406
but Mathew was
very good at his job.

24:33.440 --> 24:37.077
He actually apologized to all
